episodes.title: HONEST Interviewer RIPS Twin Flames Cult Leader in half but he’s “Sorry You Feel That Way”
episodes.description:
Husband and wife, Jeff and Shaleia Divine, founders of Twin Flames Universe, address the serious accusations they are facing in an interview with Avery Haines. Twin Flames Universe is an alleged cult that claims to help individuals find their soulmate. The couple has been highly criticized for their practices, with many former members speaking out in the docuseries "Escaping Twin Flames" about abuse, brainwashing, forced labor, coercion to alter their sexual identities, and so much more.
